    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" resp="#JP">
                <ab>                    
                    <lb n="1"/>Ῥουφείνα Μαρκία
                   <lb n="2"/>ζήσασα ἔτη <num value="35">λε</num>
                    <lb n="3"/>Σόσσις ἀνήρ ἐπόη
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>σε ἰδίᾳ γυναικί εὐσεβεσ
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>τάτη μνημεῖον
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp><app><note>Text after Zavettieri 2017 and photograph</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Rufina Marcia having lived for 35 years, her husband Sossis made this memorial for his own most pious wife</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="Zavettieri">
                <p>Rufina Marcia vissuta anni 35, il marito Sossis fece alla propria moglie piissima un monumento</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Cf. <ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic3521">ISic3521</ref> for another female member of the gens Marcia in Messina. The rare name Sossis is also attested at Catania in <ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic1324">ISic1324</ref></p>
            </div>
